Disclaimer
^^^^^^^^^^

  The  SmallCalc is a little, easy-to-use calculator, to change the original
calculator  program  of  WB3.x.   With new features, like number base system
changing  function,  or  logarithm calculating.  I am sorry, but the size is
grew  up  a little, but it is still usable, I think.  Installation and using
is very simple.  Made at Sunday, 19-dec-1995.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "installation" "SmallCalc guide - Installation"
@NEXT "legal"
@PREV "disclaimer"
@TOC "MAIN"

Installation
^^^^^^^^^^^^

  Only  copy  the  required version to a suitable sub directory on your hard
disk,  rename  it,  and  it's  ready  to  use.  For this reason, I loose the
install script from this archive.

@ENDNODE

