@NODE "usage" "SmallCalc guide - Usage"
@NEXT "future"
@PREV "author"
@TOC "MAIN"

Usage
^^^^^

  Very  easy  to  use  with  mouse,  but  most  of  functions  available  by
keystrokes.  The useful keys:

 numbers (numpad & normal)
 A-F    - Hexadecimal digits
 DEL    - Clear all (Ca)
 BCK    - Clears the last character (¨)
 +      - Plus (numpad)
 -      - Minus (numpad)
 enter  - Equal (both)
 point  - Decimal point (numpad)
 -      - Change sign (normal)
 *      - Multiple (numpad)
 /      - Division (numpad)
 TAB    - Change numeric system
 F1-F10 - memories, 0-9 (F1-mem0 ... F10-mem9)
@ENDNODE

@NODE "future" "SmallCalc guide - Future Plans"
@PREV "usage"
@TOC "MAIN"

Future Plans
^^^^^^^^^^^^

  I shall write a new calculator, with more mathematical function, more help
for  programmers,  clipboard  support, and window position save option.  The
next version will be a programmable calculator, with any number of programs.
I  want  to end this project at about marc/apr of 1996, at the same time (or
in  the  same  pack) like a multi programming language interface for GoldED.
(most of it will be ARexx macro.)



@ENDNODE

